<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sistem Ujian Online Premium</title>
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS (CDN) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <!-- FontAwesome & SweetAlert2 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>

    <style>
        /* Glassmorphism Theme & Custom CSS */
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0c3fc 0%, #8ec5fc 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.15);
        }
        .hide { display: none !important; }
        
        /* Reading Text Box for English Exam */
        .reading-text {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
            padding: 15px;
            max-height: 250px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Radio Button Styling */
        .option-label {
            display: block;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            background: white;
        }
        .option-label:hover { border-color: #a5b4fc; background: #eef2ff; }
        input[type="radio"]:checked + .option-label {
            border-color: #4f46e5;
            background: #e0e7ff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Print Media Query */
        @media print {
            body { background: white; }
            .no-print { display: none !important; }
            .glass-card { box-shadow: none; border: none; }
            table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
            th, td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-4 md:p-8">

    <!-- APP CONTAINER -->
    <div id="app-container" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Tombol Admin Kanan Atas -->
        <div id="top-admin-nav" class="flex justify-end mb-2 animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
            <button onclick="showView('view-login-admin')" class="text-xs md:text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 transition">
                <i class="fas fa-lock text-gray-600"></i> Admin
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- 1A. VIEW LOGIN SISWA (Utama) -->
        <div id="view-login" class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-md mx-auto mt-4 text-center animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap text-indigo-600"></i> Portal Ujian</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Silakan login untuk memulai ujian</p>
            
            <div class="mb-4 text-left">
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2">Username Siswa</label>
                <input type="text" id="username-siswa" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500" placeholder="Masukkan nama Anda">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 text-left">
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2">Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="password-siswa" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500" placeholder="Masukkan password">
            </div>
            <button onclick="handleLogin('siswa')" class="w-full bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 shadow-md">
                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Masuk Ujian
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- 1B. VIEW LOGIN ADMIN -->
        <div id="view-login-admin" class="hide glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-md mx-auto mt-4 text-center animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2"><i class="fas fa-user-shield text-gray-800"></i> Dashboard Admin</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Akses khusus manajemen ujian</p>
            
            <div class="mb-4 text-left">
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2">Username Admin</label>
                <input type="text" id="username-admin" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-800" placeholder="Ketik: admin">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-6 text-left">
                <label class="block text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2">Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="password-admin" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-800" placeholder="Masukkan password">
            </div>
            <button onclick="handleLogin('admin')" class="w-full bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-900 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 shadow-md mb-3">
                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Masuk Dashboard
            </button>
            <button onclick="showView('view-login')" class="w-full bg-transparent hover:bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 border border-gray-300">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Kembali ke Portal Siswa
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. VIEW PETUNJUK -->
        <div id="view-petunjuk" class="hide glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-4 border-b pb-2">Petunjuk Ujian</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                <li>Berdoalah sebelum mengerjakan soal.</li>
                <li>Waktu ujian adalah <b>60 Menit</b>. Waktu akan berjalan di pojok kanan atas.</li>
                <li><b>Peringatan Keras (Anti-Cheat Aktif):</b> Anda dilarang keluar aplikasi, membelah layar (split-screen), minimize, atau membuka tab lain. Pelanggaran akan menyebabkan ujian langsung dihentikan otomatis dan Anda dinyatakan <b>Curang</b>.</li>
                <li>Pilih satu jawaban yang paling tepat.</li>
            </ul>
            <button onclick="startExam()" class="w-full bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300 text-lg shadow-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-play-circle"></i> MULAI UJIAN SEKARANG
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. VIEW UJIAN -->
        <div id="view-ujian" class="hide glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 w-full mt-4">
            <!-- Header Ujian -->
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center border-b pb-4 mb-6 sticky top-0 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur z-10 p-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                <div class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i> <span id="student-name-display"></span></div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-red-600 mt-2 md:mt-0 flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock mr-2 animate-pulse"></i> <span id="timer-display">60:00</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Kontainer Soal -->
            <div id="question-container">
